(1, 1, 'Home Page', '<table border="0" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5" width="100%">\r\n	<tr><td class="main" width="65%" valign="top">\r\n	<strong>A little about EosC 2.2</strong>\r\n       <p> <b><font color="red">Before you do anything else login to the <a href="admin/">admin</a>, click on My Account and change the default info and password. Now. Right now. Really. Do it right now. I can wait...</font></b>  </p>\r\n       <p> All done? Alrighty then!  </p>\r\n	<p> Evolve Networks has worked hard to make this store as full featured and easy to use as possible. The 2.x edition was created with speed and extensibility in mind and, as such, doesn&#39;t follow the general trend in loaded osCommerce distributions of trying to be all things to every merchant.  </p>\r\n	<p> This edition contains only the contributions and tweaks we feel are necessary for a full featured cart that&#39;s not so far away from a stock osCommerce install as to be mind-numbingly difficult to modify.</p>\r\n	<p> In fact this edition is about as loaded as it''s going to get in order to ensure being able to modify it''s functionality and display with as little effort as possible. Evolve uses this edition as the base install for our customers. Updates to this edition will be of the speed, bug and security type only. The rest is up to you! :)\r\n	<p> EosC 2.2 comes with no strings attached. You&#39;re free to modify the template, graphics or code and redistribute it as you like as provided by the GPL.</p>\r\n	<p> Support is offered to Evolve Networks clients only. If you&#39;re not currently an Evolve customer but would like support please visit <a href="http://www.e-osc.com/">http://www.e-osc.com/</a> </p>\r\n	<p> Also be sure to stop by the osCommerce site and thank them and all the contributors for the 1000&#39;s of hours of work involved collectively in making this the best shopping cart software available!\r\n	<p> Thanks and have fun!<br /> \r\n	<a href="http://e.volve.net">Evolve Networks</a>    </p>\r\n	</td><td class="main" width="35%" valign="top"> \r\n	<strong>Installed Contributions</strong> \r\n	<p> \r\n	<li>Admin Access Levels </li>\r\n	<li>Attribute Manager &amp; Sort </li>\r\n	<li>Authorize.net AIM </li>\r\n	<li>Cart In Header </li>\r\n	<li>Coupons & Vouchers </li>\r\n	<li>Credit Card Mask </li>\r\n	<li>Cross Sell Products </li>\r\n	<li>Drop Down Button In Cart </li>\r\n	<li>Email Confirmation Field </li>\r\n	<li>Email Invoice Template </li>\r\n	<li>Featured Products </li>\r\n	<li>Header Tags Controller </li>\r\n	<li>Improved Invoice </li>\r\n	<li>LinkPoint API </li>\r\n	<li>Monthly Sales & Tax </li>\r\n	<li>Newsletters &amp; Subscribers </li>\r\n	<li>Order Editor </li>\r\n	<li>Page Editor </li>\r\n	<li>PayPal IPN </li>\r\n	<li>Product Listing Columns </li>\r\n	<li>Product Short Descriptions </li>\r\n	<li>Product Tabs & Standard Views </li>\r\n	<li>Quantity Tracker Pro </li>\r\n	<li>Register Globals Off</li>\r\n	<li>Review Approval System </li>\r\n	<li>Reviews In Product Display </li>\r\n	<li>Separate Price Per Customer </li>\r\n	<li>Shipping Estimator </li>\r\n       <li>Site Map </li>\r\n	<li>STS - Simple Template System </li>\r\n	<li>TinyMCE HTML Editor </li>\r\n	<li>Ultimate SEO URLs</li>\r\n	<li>Ultra Pics </li>\r\n	<li>UPS, USPS & FedEx Shipping </li>\r\n	<li>Whos Online Enhancement </li>\r\n	<li>PHP4/5 & mySQL 4/5 Ready</li>\r\n	<li> + many more tweaks :P  </li>\r\n</td></tr></table>'),
